 </p>

<p>From the time that we transmitted this email, you will have 96 hours to visit the website to complete the information that we require and confirm your participation.<br/> Should this time expire without us receiving your confirmation, then we will be unable to send you the wine for evaluation.</p>

<p>We look forward to receiving your confirmation of participation and postal details.</p>
